## ⚠️ Troubleshooting

### "Location not working"
- Enable location in browser settings
- Check phone location settings
- Try allowing again

### "Map not loading"
- Check internet connection
- Refresh page
- Clear browser cache

### "Admin can't login"
- Check password: `halloween2025`
- Clear browser cookies
- Try incognito/private mode

### "Auto-refresh not working"
- Make sure toggle is ON (green)
- Check if location permission granted
- Try manual update first

## 🎊 Have Fun!

This app makes trick-or-treating interactive and fun! Kids love tracking down the moving candy cart. Happy Halloween! 🎃👻🍬
